acceptApplication(address).notice: Marks an application as accepted. This function can only be called by the proposal contract.

setBudgets(uint256[]).notice: Set the budgets for the applicants. This function can only be called by the proposal contract and only during the reveal phase.  Any applicant who has submitted a budget within 10% of the proposal budget will have their budget set.

submitApplication(string,string).notice: Submit an application for the proposal. This function can only be called during the submission phase.

voteForApplication(address,uint256).notice: Vote for an application. This function can only be called by the proposal contract.
